    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Brazilian friction drums, whose membrane is perforated by a stick which is rubbed with either the player's wetted hand or a damp cloth.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
